data.title: Chelsea Clinton Welcomes a Baby Boy
data.text:
There's a very new member joining the Clinton campaign trail, and he's just a few days old! Chelsea Clinton and husband Marc Mezvinsky have welcomed a new baby, a boy named Aidan Clinton Mezvinsky. Hillary retweeted her daughter's announcement, which reads: "Marc and I are overwhelmed with gratitude and love as we celebrate the birth of our son, Aidan Clinton Mezvinsky."

X content

This content can also be viewed on the site it originates from.

The couple already have a daughter named Charlotte, who was born back in 2014. Aidan is the second grandchild of U.S. presidential candidate Hillary Clinton and her husband, former president Bill Clinton.
